<div class="box full guide">
  <p>The Battle Pet Network is a virtual pet game where you befriend, raise, adventure, and fight with evolved housecats in a post-apocalyptic world after the fall of man.</p>
  <p>At the forefront of your pet's survival is battle! You'll match wits with other players using the elegant Undercut combat system. Find rival pets and challenge them, secretly choose your pet's actions, and then see who wins as the fight resolves by comparing pet strategies.</p>

  <h4>Gameplay</h4>
  <p>The world is rich with adventure for your pet, of battle and otherwise. Some of the things you'll do together include:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Challenging and battling other pets, outwitting your foes with decisive strategies</li>
    <li>Hunting mutants, hybrids, wild humans, and defending the commonwealth of pets from the sentient menace</li>
    <li>Equipping your pet with battle gear and collectables to enhance their skills</li>
    <li>Taming savage humans with your pet's irresistible affection, then putting them to work in the kennels</li>
    <li>Scavenging the ruins for items, foraging the lands for food and treats</li>
    <li>Joining or founding a pack with other pets, to fight and glory together</li>
    <li>Opening a shop in the market and trading in treasure and goods with other pets</li>
    <li>Playing with friends, helping each other heal, and just chatting, as is the nature of social animals</li>
  </ul>
</div>

