  </p>

  <h4>Leaderboard: Manlords</h4>
  <p>Manlords are those pets who have most completely conquered the savage species of man, tamed their ranks, and kenneled their most powerful specimens. In no uncertain terms, ranking leaders have the most total power in their kennel.</p>
  <p>
  Awards:
  <ol>
