  </p>

  <h4>Leaderboard: Hordes</h4>
  <p>Hordes are the packs with the greatest accumulated power. This means the most pack members, most powerful spoils, biggest treasury, and greatest average battle record amongst its members. Only active pack members are counted when ranking the pack, however. Awards are given to the pack leader, who may then distribute it at will.</p>
