  <h4>Leaderboard: Ambassadors</h4>
  <p>The ambassadors of the world are those pets with the most number of signs, messages, forum posts, and other social activity over the last ranking period. These pets are widely known and, for better or worse, pass through the many lives of their brethren.</p>
